## Important Context Notes

1. **Singapore LTA Data** - Not London TfL (pivoted due to data accessibility)
2. **Monthly Updates** - Pipeline runs monthly when new data available (by 10th)
3. **Historical Window** - API provides 3 months history; must save monthly for longer retention
4. **Fully Automated** - No manual CSV downloads
5. **Production-Grade** - Industry best practices demonstrated
6. **Package Management** - Use `uv` exclusively (not pip)
7. **Terraform First** - Provision all cloud infrastructure before deploying code
8. **API Documentation** - Refer to LTA_DataMall_API_User_Guide.pdf for specifications
9. **Data Already Extracted** - January 2026 data already downloaded locally
10. **Infrastructure Ready** - Terraform configs created, ready for `terraform apply`
11. **GCP Project** - Using `sg-public-transport-pipeline`
12. **User Runs Commands** - Assistant suggests, user executes all terminal commands

